<HEADLINE>
CYBER ENCYCLOPEDIA: THE HIGH ROAD AT A HIGH COST 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(jt) 
 By EDWARD WYATT    
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   As Internet users stampeded to visit the Encyclopaedia
