</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    World Series mania
 &HT;    By Staff Reports
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ Hey, batter batter! The Braves are battling the
Yankees to be World Series champs. You can check out
