r w BC-TUPPERWARE-$ADV31-COX     10-25 1521
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TUPPERWARE-$ADV31-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    PRESERVED FOR POSTERITY: HOW TUPPERWARE PARTIES BEGAN
 &HT;    1000&AMP;add. Moving in (w) Washington and (l) lifestyle categories
for release Sunday, Oct. 31.
