Bourbeuse for smallmouth bass is a passion for Al Agnew of Desloge,
Mo. His passion is also painting the fishing on the stream. He
tries to transfer the beauty his sees and experiences on the rivers
to his canvas. PHOTOS, PAINTING. LOCATOR in mike fitz's wooden
mailbox.
</P>
<P>
   SERIES. World Series off-day feature as the series shifts from
Atlanta to New York. Dick Kaegel.
