<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; COMMENTARY &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; IT'S AMERICA'S WORLD. BUT HOW SHOULD THIS COLOSSUS BEHAVE? &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (1,050 words) &QL;
