<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-25 13:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7600 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k BC-MILLENNIUM-BEST-TIME-     10-25 1523
