<HEADLINE>
WILL THE INTERNET MARK A TURNING POINT FOR WOMEN?  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
   &HT;    (To purchase this ``separate buy'' article from the New York
Times Syndicate please contact syndicate sales representative DEBRA
WEYDERT at 732-390-4480)
 &HT;    
 By ESTHER DYSON  
 FROM: The New York Times Magazine  
 c.1999 Esther Dyson  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Not long ago, Ann Winblad, a successful venture capitalist well
known on the high-tech circuit, stood up to speak at a conference.
