   ARGENTINA-ASSESS (Buenos Aires) _ A news analysis on the
election of a non-Peronist as Argentina's new president: It may be
viewed as both a vote for change and for continuity; sort of a
throw the (corrupt) bums out, but keep their policies. By Clifford
Krauss.
</P>
