<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-25 15:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7815 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r l BC-PUMPKIN-CARVING-LADN &LR;      10-25 1039
