Republicans to block President Clinton's nominees they don't like,
Democratic Senator Barbara Boxer has turned the tables. Now she's
blocking a nominee favored by Senate Majority Leader Trent Lott
until the Republicans agree to consider two Californians she is
backing. By JUDY HOLLAND.
</P>
