decent thing to do when I inquired of my family, ``Does anyone want
to go shopping with me and my sister today?'' Keep in mind that I
have three males in my family, none of whom are particularly
enthusiastic shoppers. Shopping is not even in my Top 10 list of
things to do, but occasionally the primal urge hits me and I have
to act on it. By MONICA ANDERSON. Story will move in ``l''
