   HOCKEY
</P>
<P>
   HKN-FLAMES _ ATLANTA _ The Flames are back, 19 seasons after
they left Atlanta for Calgary. The Thrashers host the Flames at
Philips Arena on Tuesday, with plenty of old Atlanta hockey fans
watching their old team play their new team. The game brings back
memories for former goalie Dan Bouchard, who played all eight
seasons in Atlanta and then moved with the Flames to Calgary in
1980. (Schultz, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 16.
