<SLUG> BC-GLF-CRASH-SCENE-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
FAITH AND FAMILY LED STEWART'S PRIORITIES 

</HEADLINE>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  (Eds.: Filed in ``a'' and ``s'' categories) 
 
By EDDIE SEFKO 
c.1999 Houston Chronicle 
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   HOUSTON _ When professional golfer Dennis Paulson's airplane
touched down Monday in Houston, he instinctively did what he always
