   ``If Payne had asked me to hop on the plane with him, I probably
would have,'' Waldorf said. ``This just makes you think of all the
times you've ever flown on an airplane. As pro golfers, we fly
everywhere. You never think of it as being a risky thing.
</P>
<P>
   ``I guess what you have to realize is that every day could be
your last. So you'd better live it to the fullest.''
</P>
<P>
   The entire golf world felt Monday like Stewart got shortchanged
in days.
</P>
<P>
   ``You feel like you've lost a big part of the game,'' Waldorf
said. ``It's not something you can expect. And it's hard to deal
with. You're not used to having one of your good friends die.
</P>
<P>
   ``We'll never be able to replace Payne.''
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
XXXX END OF STORY &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
